#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><b>Appointments App</b>: </strong>Organize and book winery tours and "
"tastings, enhancing the visitor\n"
"                    experience."
msgstr ""
"<strong><b>预约应用程序</b>： </strong>组织和预订酒庄参观和品酒活动，提升游"
"客\n"
"                    体验。"

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><b>CRM App</b>: </strong>Cultivate relationships with distributors "
"and private clients, tracking leads\n"
"                    to close more deals effectively.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><b>CRM 应用程序</b>： </strong>培养与分销商和私人客户的关系，追踪线"
"索\n"
"，有效达成更多交易。<br/>"

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><b>Field Service App</b>: </strong>Coordinate vineyard operations, "
"assigning tasks to teams for pruning,\n"
"                    spraying, and harvesting.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><b>现场服务应用程序</b>： </strong>协调葡萄园作业，为修剪、\n"
"喷洒和采摘团队分配任务。<br/>"

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><b>Manufacturing App</b>: </strong>Manage the art of winemaking by "
"overseeing pressing, fermentation,\n"
"                    and blending processes with precision.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><b>制造应用程序</b>： </strong>通过精确监督压榨、发酵、\n"
"和调配过程，管理酿酒艺术。<br/>"

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><b>PLM App</b>: </strong>Innovate your wine portfolio by iterating "
"on blend recipes and managing product\n"
"                    lifecycle changes.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><b>PLM 应用程序</b>： </strong>通过迭代调配配方和管理产品\n"
"生命周期变化，创新您的葡萄酒产品组合。<br/> <br/>"

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><b>Point of Sale App</b>: </strong>Manage direct sales at the cellar "
"door with an easy-to-use interface\n"
"                    for visitors and tourists.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><b>销售点应用程序</b>： </strong>通过简单易用的界面管理酒窖门口的直接"
"销售，\n"
"，供游客和访客使用。<br/>"

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><b>Quality App</b>: </strong>Ensure every bottle meets your "
"standards by tracking quality control points\n"
"                    throughout production.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><b>品控应用程序</b>： </strong>在整个生产过程中跟踪质量控制点\n"
"，确保每瓶酒都符合您的标准。<br/>"

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong><b>Website App</b>: </strong>Sell your wines globally with a fully "
"integrated eCommerce platform that\n"
"                    manages inventory in real-time.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><b>网站管理应用程序</b>： </strong>通过完全整合的电子商务平台（\n"
"）实时管理库存，在全球范围内销售您的葡萄酒。<br/>"

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Accept multiple payment methods</strong> (cash, card)."
msgstr "<strong>接受多种付款方式</strong>（现金、银行卡）。"

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Accounting</strong> – Manage finances, track profitability by "
"product line, and automate reporting."
msgstr "<strong>会计</strong> - 管理财务、按产品线追踪盈利情况并自动生成报告。"

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Add products</strong> to POS catalog."
msgstr "<strong>向 POS 目录添加产品</strong>。"

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Analyze trends</strong> for planning through reporting."
msgstr "<strong>分析趋势</strong>，通过报告进行排期。"

#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Apply taxes</strong> automatically on invoices."
msgstr "自动在发票上<strong>应用税项</strong>。"

