#. module: vineyard
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:vineyard.ir_ui_view_4048
msgid ""
"Your visit ends with a <strong>guided tasting</strong> of our signature "
"creations, including the bold <strong>Bordoo Grand Cru</strong>, the vibrant "
"<strong>Odoomatic Spice</strong>, and the elegant <strong>Pinodoo Noir</"
"strong>. Each sip tells a story of passion, craftsmanship, and the unique "
"terroir that defines our vineyard."
msgstr ""
"本次品鉴之旅的尾声，我们将为你带来酒庄招牌佳酿的<strong>专业品鉴导赏</"
"strong>，品鉴酒款包括酒体醇厚的<strong>波尔多列级酒庄酒</strong>、鲜活饱满的 "
"<strong>Odoomatic</strong> 辛香风味酒，以及格调雅致的<strong>黑皮诺杜葡萄酒</"
"strong>。每一口品鉴，都诉说着一份匠心热忱、精湛工艺，还有造就本酒庄独特风格的"
"风土底蕴。"

